# @COMMENT: This passage is similar to one located in WZATB (HSNXV02P373C). Also see WYBWS, in both the fragmentary form found in WSACD, and as a part of a much longer narrative. WMSAH and WSFAB include versions that embed them in longer accounts similar to that found in WYBWS. The passage above is worded slightly differently from WMSAH and WSFAB. @EC_01/28/23@ 

# @SFTXV01P087B_BEG_WBSAB نا بكر عن ابن إسحاق عن الزهري عن عبيد الله بن عبد الله بن عتبة قال خرج رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم لعشر خلون من شهر رمضان يريد مكة. @SFTXV01P087B_END_WBSAB
PageV01P087
# @COMMENT: This fragment is similar to that that found in WZATB on HSNXV02P437C that closes the story of Khālid b. al-Walīd’s mission to destroy the image of al-ʿUzzā at Nakhlah, but includes reference to the year. It is part of a compund clause in WSACD. This clasue is also found as a stand alone fragments in WSACD (see ZTKXV01P096A). A similar passage is also found in WAIYA and WSFAB. Placement based on initial reference in the first clause. @EC_01/31/23@

